Package edu.rit.aes

Package edu.rit.aes contains implementations of the AES family of block ciphers for testing by the CryptoStat library.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AES128
    Class AES128 implements the AES block cipher with a 128-bit key.
    AES192
    Class AES192 implements the AES block cipher with a 192-bit key.
    AES256
    Class AES256 implements the AES block cipher with a 256-bit key.
    AESBase
    Class AESBase is the abstract base class for the AES block cipher.
